---

<section class="value-props">
	<div class="container">

		<p class="section-label reveal">— WHY WORK WITH US</p>

		<div class="props-grid">

			<!-- 01 — We Win Together -->
			<div class="prop reveal">
				<div class="prop-icon" aria-hidden="true">
					<svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<!-- Two lines converging upward — shared apex -->
						<line x1="5" y1="30" x2="18" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<line x1="31" y1="30" x2="18" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<!-- Small dot at apex -->
						<circle cx="18" cy="8" r="1.75" fill="currentColor"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="prop-headline">We Win Together</h3>
				<p class="prop-body">
					We work for cash and carry. When your valuation moves, so does ours. That's not a tagline — it's the only model that keeps an advisor honest.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- 02 — The Market Isn't Waiting -->
			<div class="prop reveal">
				<div class="prop-icon" aria-hidden="true">
					<svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<!-- Diagonal momentum arrow -->
						<line x1="5" y1="28" x2="28" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<!-- Arrowhead -->
						<line x1="28" y1="8" x2="16" y2="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<line x1="28" y1="8" x2="28" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="prop-headline">The Market Isn't Waiting</h3>
				<p class="prop-body">
					The market is writing your story right now, whether you are or not. Fast-growing companies can't afford to miss a quarter — and a blurry narrative is how quarters get missed.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- 03 — Built Where You're Building -->
			<div class="prop reveal">
				<div class="prop-icon" aria-hidden="true">
					<svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<!-- Schematic lines — blueprint aesthetic -->
						<line x1="5" y1="12" x2="31" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<line x1="5" y1="19" x2="24" y2="19" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<line x1="5" y1="26" x2="17" y2="26" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="prop-headline">Built Where You're Building</h3>
				<p class="prop-body">
					We come from companies that scaled through exactly the stages you're in. We know the playbooks — and more importantly, we know when to throw them out.
				</p>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.value-props {
		background: var(--green-dark);
		padding: 7rem 0 8rem;
	}

	.section-label {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.28em;
		color: rgba(237, 236, 227, 0.4);
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.props-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(237, 236, 227, 0.1);
	}

	.prop {
		padding: 3rem 3rem 3rem 0;
		border-right: 1px solid rgba(237, 236, 227, 0.1);
	}

	.prop:first-child {
		padding-left: 0;
	}

	.prop:not(:first-child) {
		padding-left: 3rem;
	}

	.prop:last-child {
		border-right: none;
		padding-right: 0;
	}

	/* Icon */
	.prop-icon {
		color: var(--orange);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		display: block;
	}

	/* Headline */
	.prop-headline {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2vw, 1.85rem);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1;
		color: var(--white);
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
	}

	/* Body */
	.prop-body {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: rgba(237, 236, 227, 0.55);
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* ── Responsive ──────────────────────────── */
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.props-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.prop,
		.prop:not(:first-child),
		.prop:last-child {
			padding: 2.75rem 0;
			border-right: none;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(237, 236, 227, 0.1);
		}

		.prop:last-child {
			border-bottom: none;
		}

		.value-props { padding: 5rem 0 6rem; }
	}
</style>
